  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611940/extras/cdceba6e1c9c2a7539c288ca1beaf18f.avif?t=1735234300\" width=616 height=176 /></span><br><br><strong>Welcome to Driveland! </strong>You decide how you want to spend your time on the road. Will you take on the role of a dedicated delivery driver, farmer, maybe become a taxi driver? Or do you want to oppose mediocrity and associate with the bad guys, taking the lead across the island? Call a friend, you might need some help.<br><br><strong>Enjoy a relaxing and captivating atmosphere!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611940/extras/000d89074b1db5d31db34582a045d348.avif?t=1735234300\" width=616 height=176 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611940/extras/fde08c99794b584f213b556431ac4ed8.avif?t=1735234300\" width=616 height=176 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Realistic driving experience, with advanced physics simulation<br></li><li>Vehicle repair, upgrade, refueling and other realistic features<br></li><li>Open world map divided into several zones<br></li><li>Single-player and Multiplayer(Alpha) modes<br></li><li>Day & Night cycle, with different weather conditions<br></li><li>Many activities (Racing, passenger / cargo transportation, special missions and events)<br></li><li>Interactable NPCs<br></li><li>Multiple missions (more or less legal)<br></li><li>Online stats and achievements</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611940/extras/30bfce367d3f3ef6d942d4c442d6edf1.avif?t=1735234300\" width=616 height=176 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611940/extras/cdceba6e1c9c2a7539c288ca1beaf18f.avif?t=1735234300\" width=616 height=176 /></span><br><br><strong>Welcome to Driveland! </strong>You decide how you want to spend your time on the road. Will you take on the role of a dedicated delivery driver, farmer, maybe become a taxi driver? Or do you want to oppose mediocrity and associate with the bad guys, taking the lead across the island? Call a friend, you might need some help.<br><br><strong>Enjoy a relaxing and captivating atmosphere!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611940/extras/000d89074b1db5d31db34582a045d348.avif?t=1735234300\" width=616 height=176 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611940/extras/fde08c99794b584f213b556431ac4ed8.avif?t=1735234300\" width=616 height=176 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Realistic driving experience, with advanced physics simulation<br></li><li>Vehicle repair, upgrade, refueling and other realistic features<br></li><li>Open world map divided into several zones<br></li><li>Single-player and Multiplayer(Alpha) modes<br></li><li>Day & Night cycle, with different weather conditions<br></li><li>Many activities (Racing, passenger / cargo transportation, special missions and events)<br></li><li>Interactable NPCs<br></li><li>Multiple missions (more or less legal)<br></li><li>Online stats and achievements</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611940/extras/30bfce367d3f3ef6d942d4c442d6edf1.avif?t=1735234300\" width=616 height=176 /></span>",
